data.text:
The League of Women Voters of California is a nonpartisan, grassroots organization working to protect and expand voting rights, build grassroots power in our communities, drive policy change on the biggest challenges facing our state, and ensure everyone is represented in our democracy.

These are difficult times to hold on to our resolve, but we are the League of Women Voters. Resolve is in our DNA. Please give to the LWVC Action Fund today so, together, we can keep bringing the Leagueâ€™s voice and influence to all of the policy work needed to build a better future . Now is not the time for us to back down.
